  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"1.1.0-alpha01\" data-text=\"Version 1.1.0-alpha01\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.1.0-alpha01</h3>\n<p>August 5, 2020</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.enterprise:enterprise-feedback:1.1.0-alpha01</code> and <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.enterprise:enterprise-feedback-testing:1.1.0-alpha01</code> are released. <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/825d4a371a29f073d46f219936f7ef0f6e5f437d..316f882e649c600372170f013a18515f590f490d/enterprise/feedback\">Version 1.1.0-alpha01 contains these commits.</a></p>\n<p><strong>API Changes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Replaced constants for max field sizes with getters. (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/I2e351b47a2ed16adfc0545fb9b1d7a3343b8bb92\">I2e351</a>, <a href=\"https://issuetracker.google.com/issues/140519786\">b/140519786</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Now compatible with apps targeting API 30</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"version_100_3\" data-text=\"Version 1.0.0\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.0.0</h2>",
